AppLog
======

A very simple plugin that allows you to log in a separate file (log/application.log by default)


Install
=======
script/plugin install git://github.com/hgtesta/app-log.git


Example
=======

AppLog returns a Logger object.

AppLog.info "Process finished."
AppLog.warn "User login failed."

